#   | observability-engineer       | @Extr3sao/observability-team   |
#   | security-reviewer            | @Extr3sao/security-team        |
#
# ===========================================================================
# PRE-FLIGHT OBLIGATORIO antes de mergear este archivo a main:
#
#   gh api /orgs/Extr3sao/teams --jq '.[].slug'
#
# Si el comando anterior NO devuelve TODOS los 10 slugs (los 9 mapeados
